---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LanguageSwitch from '../../components/LanguageSwitch.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout lang={lang} title="Privacy Policy - Giovanna Niola" description="Information on the processing of personal data">
  <Fragment slot="langswitch"><LanguageSwitch lang={lang} /></Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="langswitch-mobile"><LanguageSwitch lang={lang} /></Fragment>
  
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose prose-lg">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB')}</p>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>
        The Data Controller for personal data is <strong>Giovanna Niola</strong>, 
        Cognitive Behavioural Psychotherapist, registered with the Order of Psychologists of Sardinia (1/SPS).
      </p>
      <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@niolaterapia.com" class="underline">info@niolaterapia.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">2. Data Collected</h2>
      <p>Through this website, we collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Voluntarily provided data:</strong> name, email address, and message content sent via the contact form.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> necessary for the correct functioning of the website (e.g., standard server logs).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>Data is processed to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Respond to contact requests</li>
        <li>Manage appointment scheduling</li>
        <li>Provide psychotherapy services</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">4. Legal Basis</h2>
      <p>
        The processing is based on the <strong>explicit consent</strong> of the data subject (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR) 
        and on the <strong>execution of pre-contractual measures</strong> adopted at the request of the data subject (Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Data will be retained for the time strictly necessary for the purposes for which it was collected 
        and in compliance with legal obligations (for clinical data: 10 years from the conclusion of treatment, 
        as required by the Code of Ethics for Psychologists).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">6. Communication and Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data will not be shared with third parties or disclosed, except for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Legal obligations</li>
        <li>Necessary technical services (Formspree for email delivery)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">7. Rights of the Data Subject</h2>
      <p>Pursuant to Arts. 15-22 of the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Obtain rectification or erasure of the data</li>
        <li>Obtain restriction of processing</li>
        <li>Object to the processing</li>
        <li>Request data portability</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with the Data Protection Authority</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">
        To exercise your rights, please contact: <a href="mailto:giovannaniola@gmail.com" class="underline">giovannaniola@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">8. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not use profiling or analytical cookies. 
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
       It only uses technical elements necessary for the basic functioning of the site and the contact form.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-4">9. Changes to this Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This policy may be updated periodically. The date of the last update is indicated at the top of this page.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border">
      <p class="text-sm">
        <strong>Questions or concerns?</strong> For any clarification regarding privacy and data processing, 
        please do not hesitate to contact me at <a href="mailto:info@niolaterapia.com" class="underline">info@niolaterapia.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
